# sensors/actors pipeline scratch artifacts (issue #56) — these are produced at
# the repo root by the weekly workflows (gather/draft/validate/claim outputs) and
# must never be committed into an auto-land PR. Ignoring them keeps `git add -A`
# in the drift-actor workflow from sweeping scratch JSON into the diff.
/signal.json
/state.json
/patch.json
/claim.json
/proposal.json
/facts.json
/draft.json
/seeds.json
/notebook-raw.json
/validated-seeds.json
